    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Whenever the sage uses the ability granted by the enhancer esoteric training package to grant himself a bonus to one or more of his physical ability scores, he may spend a ki point to gain regeneration 1 for the duration of the effect. At 4th level and every 4 levels thereafter, this regeneration increases by an additional 1. Taking damage from ki effects (such as a ki blast, chi gong touch attack, or any damaging effect that requires the user to expend 1 or more ki points to activate) suppresses this regeneration for 1 round.</p>\n",
